{"tid":21948,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"(選科過來人)讀大學，請揀最實用最有挑戰性既科！！！！！","createTime":"2016-12-04T07:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T07:08:47.000Z","uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e4a9f13eff827ae5fb59c8ce1494ee68f044186","tid":21948,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:02:14.000Z","msg":"實用既原則分為兩點，其一係讀左之後定必定與職場相關，例如Civil/EE/Mechanical讀完必定做專業工程師；Poly五寶就必定做物治師／職治師等；醫科護理必成醫生護士。其二係實用要根據學科既可靠性為本，最可靠既係數學、邏輯，係所有野既根基，繼而係科學類如物理／化學／生物，不太可靠為社會學科。因此，Engineering最具可靠同實用既優勢，而不可靠既文科社科因為太多學混同垃圾人文理論，優勢盡失。<br />\n<br />\n另外，學科有挑戰性有更大既優勢，可以訓練強大既解難能力、壓力處理能力、邏輯分析力等，在職場上會有好大既優勢。因此，難讀既科如工程、醫療五寶會相對上比19BBA、文科社科會更好。<br />\n<br />\n結論：Engineering~Medicine&gt;五寶&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;19BBA~Science&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;SocSci~文科 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家真係死都唔好揀文科社科，各位巴絲有咩意見？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6c8d6a6f3e5982fe567c44da5307d4927c48bd","tid":21948,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:03:20.000Z","msg":"收嗲唔屌你老母"},{"pid":"5a619eab722e5f6281ccb16d535f2db2d11da249","tid":21948,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收嗲啦屌你老母</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8bf856b0c606cdaef271718681e83e70745e59ee","tid":21948,"uid":10094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:05:03.000Z","msg":"Mechanical讀完必定做專業工程師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4c4ea50cb4af6843666021a1c06ce302282d1d","tid":21948,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:07:25.000Z","msg":"收皮啦n賤狗"},{"pid":"29b3e41843bb76713674a707300a768f5ca90ac6","tid":21948,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:08:47.000Z","msg":"樓主我叫你收嗲呀柒頭"}]}